reviews.review_text: Tainted by Dayjob Another good show tainted by a Dayjob encore. I remember seeing one of the best second sets of my touring (11/1/85 Richmond)and than they did Dayjob as the encore. Most of the people, including me, just started laughing and walked out. The Dead could play some great shows, but encores were never their strong point! It was rare that the show was very good and so was the encore.
